WEBVTT

00:00.131 --> 00:04.913
Try giving short, simple answers. Mrs.
Griffin, what do you plan to do about crime in our

00:04.953 --> 00:06.994
city? A lot.

00:09.996 --> 00:19.861
Because that's what Jesus wants. 9-11 was bad. I
agree with that. What are your plans for

00:19.921 --> 00:30.215
cleaning up our environment? 9-11. What about
our traffic problem? Nine. Eleven.
